				<h1 class="shead-style text-center">TELENGANA</h1>
				<p>Formerly ruled by the Nizams it was also named as Hyderabad during their rule. In the recent years it is the newest state in India after separating from the former state of Andhra Pradesh. A land inhabited a long time ago is one of the most important and strategic lands in India. Ruled by various rulers throughout the history the place is rich in culture, tradition, architecture, monuments and diversity.
        </p><p>Many of the kings and dynasties who have ruled this region have contributed considerably to the society in terms of architecture and arts. One of the first cities in India to have a planned sewage system Hyderabad has many marvelous sculptures like Charminar, Palace of Nizam and Mecca Masjid etc. A visit to Telangana definitely shows you the wonders that are neither hidden nor lost through all these years.
        </p>
